---
title: Cheese and Shredded Chicken Fajitas with zingy tomato salsa
description: Tangy onion salsa, fragrant shredded carrot and aioli-coated chicken—this recipe has something to suit every taste. The DIY nature of this dish s something the whole house is sure to love.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R18_W43_IE_IEFQC13680-3_Main_high-a239a044.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipecards/card/64dc869a4f680d5c246cdad9.pdf
